/**
 * @defgroup stdio_stream_api stdio_stream API
 * @ingroup stream_family_group
 *
 * @brief Standard-stream-backed adapter for the `stream` port.
 *
 * The `stdio_stream` adapter implements the `stream` port on top of the C
 * standard I/O streams:
 * - `stdin`
 * - `stdout`
 * - `stderr`
 *
 * It is intended to expose these process-standard streams through the generic
 * `stream` abstraction.
 *
 * Sub-APIs:
 * - @ref stdio_stream_cr_api
 */
